    <briefdescription>
<para><ref refid="namespaceImageLoader" kindref="compound">ImageLoader</ref> - <ref refid="namespaceAsync" kindref="compound">Async</ref> image loading with LRU caching. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Named <ref refid="namespaceImageLoader" kindref="compound">ImageLoader</ref> instead of ImageCache to avoid conflict with juce::ImageCache.</para>
<para>Features:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para><ref refid="namespaceAsync" kindref="compound">Async</ref> loading from URLs (doesn&apos;t block <ref refid="namespaceUI" kindref="compound">UI</ref> thread)</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>LRU eviction when cache is full</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Placeholder support while loading</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Automatic retry on failure</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Thread-safe</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Drawing helpers for avatars</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para>Usage: // Load image asynchronously <ref refid="namespaceImageLoader_1a291ac43216d03d28c0b2f61c1b77f8a5" kindref="member">ImageLoader::load</ref>(url, [this](const juce::Image&amp; img) { avatarImage = img; repaint(); }); </para>
    </detaileddescription>
